===Etymology===
From {{etyl|xno}} {{term|Espayne|lang=xno}}, from {{etyl|LL.}} {{term|Spania|lang=la}}, from earlier {{etyl|la}} {{term|Hispania|Hispānia|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|grc}} {{term|tr=Hispania|Ἱσπανία|lang=grc}}, from {{etyl|phn}} {{term|tr=i-shaphanim|lang=phn|sc=Phnx|lit=[[hyrax]] isle}}, as the native wild rabbits were mistaken for hyraces.

